# General configuration 

browser "google-chrome %u"    
text-width 80
feed-sort-order unreadarticlecount-asc

# Colors

color background color188 color237
color info color223 color234
color article color188 color237
color listnormal color188 color237
color listfocus color223 color234
color listnormal_unread color108 color237 
color listfocus_unread color224 color237

highlight article "^Feed:" color108  default
highlight article "^Title:" color108 default
highlight article "^Author:" color108 default 
highlight article "^Link:" color108 default
highlight article "^Date:" color108 default
highlight article "\\[[0-9][0-9]*\\]" color021 color237 
highlight article "\\[image [0-9][0-9]*\\]" color109 default bold
highlight article "\\[embedded flash: [0-9][0-9]*\\]" color66 default bold

# Keybindings

bind-key j down feedlist
bind-key k up feedlist
bind-key j next articlelist
bind-key k prev articlelist 
